Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙穴 打开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(595,655)\fs30}Neidhöhle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：法芙娜的出击口 共32门 原意为「嫉妒之穴」 是变成巨龙的法夫纳看守财宝的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击口 坐标(32,06)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(635,655)\fs30}grid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这呢 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕登场！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 十字阵形 就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,655)\fs30}cross dog
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows 归航刚瑠岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows呼叫CDC 运输机移交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(795,655)\fs30}Track hand over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫Arrows 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cetus由CDC继续引导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫CDC 请批准Mk.Ⅶ出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将Mk.Ⅶ移至刚瑠岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅸ 上前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 准备迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,655)\fs30}scepter ready
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请准备进行同步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CDC批准了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我们这一代最后的常规驾驶员了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在两分钟内开动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要利用就利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你负责后方支援 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要连一骑的工作都揽过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…你并没有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 Mk.Ⅴ 上前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Nicht？连Mk.Sein都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些被封存的机体要纠缠我们到什么时候…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝同步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让它们干涉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我存在于此刻的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时隔四年半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一次和驾驶员共享痛觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内部被侵食 无法止痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(785,655)\fs30}Pain block
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制切断 左臂坏死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(770,655)\fs30}necrosis
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把敌人逼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申请进行饱和攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后撤到防线08 动作快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光学 热力 电波 电子 音波探测 无反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 回转体的气压发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅶ 捕捉目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 开始迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,655)\fs30}scepter go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花招不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据所罗门的分析 敌人的内核只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余的都是虚像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚像？可是它们能攻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 互相掩护啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Cetus 我们也参战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起击退威胁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军 三部法芙娜前往彦岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要共同作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一号机负责上空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二号机掩护喷火的那部机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}torch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和挥剑的那部一起作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算可以战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在那样的高速运动中打中了？好高超的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 来帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部机体是靠头部进行攻击的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没法和你们相互理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认敌人已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门系统发出应答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 阵内 我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Festum…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么…这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们放进来了一个相当重要的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎接来访者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么 收队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那些人不可信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭乘法芙娜的时间越长 就越会被同化现象侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去体检
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 没事吧 晖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他们回来就要开总结会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先体检
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是眼睁睁在一旁看着 很难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达D岛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的Mir是空气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它接纳我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最新机体就这么报废了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你能捡回一条命就算赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 将陵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看家辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把部队当什么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还把真矢也拖下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把指挥工作全丢给阵内 正经点干活行不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前真是抱歉了 将陵参谋长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人类军总务部的那雷恩·魏茨曼·玻色上将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(784,655)}Narain Weizmann Bose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们的接纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是龙宫岛Alvis司令官 真壁史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在人类军的部队是由将校率领的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在光是上将就有一百人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军衔已经成了摆设
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能由生命和希望尚存的人承担起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了确保你们不能使用武力 我们要监视法芙娜驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员就是他们三人 还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开得动？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上最高龄驾驶员的身份是我小小的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您允许驾驶员之间的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是真壁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 他不是真壁一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 超级王牌驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给了我们真壁因子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是破坏了北极Mir的驾驶员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D岛的真壁一骑 是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没怎么 就是想看看它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经战斗得足够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部Mk.Sein没人开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它太特别了 别人都开不动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划在成功取出内核之后就把它沉到海底
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西想要驾驶员的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再靠近它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是劝也劝不动 我就跟你来硬的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手 真暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 打扰你了 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗后来瓶这个真是棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想不当驾驶员了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是一想到下次就得轮到后辈上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又觉得不能不做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟剑司前辈那时也是为了我们而一直坚持开法芙娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇痛剂打多了会成瘾的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见医生说如果还是会痛 就和晖一起接受脉冲治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 美羽在Alvis吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是要让她和人类军见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听 听说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见 快穿衣服 穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个羞什么呢 是不是医生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是还嫩着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就行了啦 乖乖等一等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家等好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就相信你在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定 肯定不是我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们天各一方时就在互相交流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是通过Mir的中介而引发的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说Mir？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Festum的思维中枢 可以化为万物的万能结构体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你们对它应该更为了解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩也能与Mir交流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她弟弟似乎在机缘巧合之下得到了Mir的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是幸存下来的北极Mir的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉说是她弟弟教给了她和那块碎片交流的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的弟弟现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天 她居住的城市变成了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她弟弟通过Mir的碎片劝导对方停止杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和Festum对话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她的弟弟和家人则被Mir同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有她一个人活了下来 至今仍不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 像她这样能够和Mir交流的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们称之为「通识者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,655)\fs30}Esperanto
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：Esperanto是世界语的名字 而这个词在世界语中的意思即「希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 这个词是人类创造出的人工语言的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为相互理解 消除纷争而创造的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是真正的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然已经开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店街那边都还没开始营业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该多休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家体检完后就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沟口先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人订外卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要开会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了啦 我去就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑…在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阵内先生 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据真壁司令的指示 我们带客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的指示？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫艾西瓦娅·费因 是珀耳修斯中队的法芙娜驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(391,655)}Aishwarya Fein
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我小艾 真壁一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫比利·摩根 是个驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(573,655)}Billy Morgan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是珀耳修斯中队法芙娜队队长 乔纳森·光弘·巴特蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(930,655)}Jonathan Mitsuhiro Bertrand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到传说中的英雄 真是不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你 我才能够战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 多亏了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了 没想到真的能见到真壁因子的提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,655)\fs30}presence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将会懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的希望的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不一定意味着和平的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要守护还等同于战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望也就还处在纷争之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们冒着失去一切的风险寻求着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的任何道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都没有余地选择
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
